originalText.text: There is no customer service at all with employees from this place. I parked in the parking lot for brunch on a Saturday but had to pick up the car about an hour earlier than the pick up time that I had told them. The African employee started complaining that he has to move many cars because I came to pick up early as he made his way to pick up the car and continued to make complaints after handing over the car. I found out that he wrote down 7 pm for the pick-up time during an argument that wr made which is false fact since I had told him 3 pm is the pick-up time twice when the car was dropped off. However, he continued to blame me and told me that he was just explaining to save my time. Very disrespectful employees and I highly do not recommend making encounters with the parking lot or its employees.

originalText.text: This place is terrible. I almost never write reviews but I was so upset when I left this parking garage I needed to do something. I was yelled by the parking attendant when trying to figure out how to get a stroller to my car. The walk way was blocked and when I asked about unblocking it he yelled at me - this was totally unprovoked and I honestly couldn't believe how rude and awful they were.
